✅ Day 1 – GitHub Task List (One-Liners)
Create public GitHub repo arogya-saathi-ai

Setup folder structure: /backend and /frontend

Add .gitignore (Python + Node + Expo rules)

Initialize FastAPI in /backend/main.py

Create OCR function in /backend/services/ocr.py

Create simplify function using GPT in /backend/services/simplify.py

Build /upload API endpoint (upload → OCR → simplify → return)

Add requirements.txt after pip freeze

Create basic React Native project in /frontend using Expo

Add UploadScreen.js with image picker + fetch POST to backend

Test image upload → see simplified result in frontend

Commit all changes with clear messages

Push code to GitHub

Update README.md with project overview + setup steps

Optional: Add one sample test report image in /sample_data/